text: You seem even more excited than usual, Meguru.

Hahaha! You caught me...!
But it's because it's the first time debuting in this outfit...!

I'm looking forward to everyone seeing this cute outfit,
and also delivering songs in this outfit...!

Yeah, that's right...
We're the cheerleaders who cheer everyone up.

I hope they can be someone's feelings, and I hope
they can support everyone's everyday from tomorrow.

...Yeah, we can do it.
If it's Meguru, Mano, and Hiori.

Yeah...!
Well then, here I go!
